         <abstract id="aspace_8b47ed7c3053850cc29bb553ae74ee50">The papers consist of manuscripts, typescripts, and pre-publication versions of Ripley's writings on birds of Asia and other parts of the world. Also included is film footage of Ripley's 1948 trip to Nepal.</abstract>
